[size=3][b]Requirements[/b][/size]
[list]
[*]Anomaly 1.5.3
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stalkeranomaly/mods/102]xlibs[/url] 1.5.1+
[*]MCM
[/list]

[size=3][b]Install (MO2)[/b][/size]
[list=1]
[*]Install xlibs.
[*]Install AlifeBalance.
[*]Load order does not matter.
[*]Configure via MCM.
[/list]

[size=3][b]Uninstall[/b][/size]
Disable or remove in MO2.

